snippet.title: Etrian Odyssey Origins Collection — Announcement Trailer | Nintendo Switch, Steam
snippet.description:
Explore the beginnings of Etrian Odyssey with three remastered, timeless adventures! No journey is the same: lead a guild of adventurers and search for treasures within vast, sprawling labyrinths. 🗺️

Etrian Odyssey Origins Collection releases June 1st, 2023 for Nintendo Switch and Steam.   

Pre-order Etrian Odyssey Origins Collection now: atlus.com/etrianorigins   

Etrian Odyssey HD, Etrian Odyssey II HD and Etrian Odyssey III HD are also available for pre-order individually.
